window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Winner of the 2024 ITW Thriller Award for Best E-book Original Novel</b></p> <p><b>From </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> bestselling author Robert Swartwood comes another bone-chilling thriller that will keep you on guessing until the very last word.</b></p> <p>While on vacation in Las Vegas, a businessman wakes up in a strange hotel room to find a dead woman in the bathtub.</p> <p>Panicked, he runs. But before he can get far, a pair of detectives stop him.</p> <p>Desperate, he tells them that he’s innocent. That there’s no way he killed the woman. That he’ll do anything not to go to prison.</p> <p>That’s when they offer him a way out.</p> <p>But there is no way out—as the detectives will soon learn.</p> <p>Perfect for fans of Lee Child, Michael Sloan, and Robert Crais, <i>The Killing Room</i> races listeners from one revelation to the next at breathtaking speed.</p>"; 
